			<div class="content" id="post-content-4712024">
									

<p>Well I'm always on the lookout for new cannons. It's the easiest way to engage in a fully told story on this wiki. Of course even the best of cannons tend to spill out, but that's not really a bad thing. This one seems a bit concerning though, the absolute scale of content to do with Sarkicism on the wiki threatens to make a cannon based on their story susceptible to many misunderstandings, with new authors for the cannon eager to refrence their favorite Sarkic stories. I can think of a few stories like that off the top of my head that would be pretty antithetical to the point of this cannon, but for now this hasn't happened.</p>
<p>Who am I to judge though? I've no experience with the daunting challenge of managing a cannon. I'll be back.</p>
<p>All can be good in the world.</p>

